{
  "clauseRiskSummary": "This clause defines the subject matter of the joint venture, but does not address critical aspects like financial responsibilities, risk allocation, or dispute resolution mechanisms.",
  "operative_text": "3. PRODUCT: \"Product \" BOSCH\" has acquired, developed and continues to develop, a business using proprietary \"Nano Printed Lights\", and associated other products (the \"Products\"). BOSCH calls this Nano Printed Lights product \"Printed LightSheets\" which is considered the \"Product Name\".",
  "concerns": [
    {
      "text": "This clause lacks clarity on financial responsibilities, risk allocation, and dispute resolution mechanisms. It does not address how costs will be allocated in case of disputes or what happens if one party fails to meet its obligations.",
      "severity": "major",
      "references": ["3. PRODUCT"]
    }
  ],
  "favoursWhom": "neutral"
}

